data.description: Welcome to your new sanctuary! Situated on an expansive corner lot, this 3-bedroom, 2 bathroom home exudes contemporary elegance and thoughtful design. Built in 2022, this home also features a bonus room, offering versatility as an additional bedroom or a home office, while a separate laundry room adds practicality to your daily routine.  Entertain with ease in the open-plan living room and gourmet kitchen that will delight any chef. Quartz countertops, a kitchen island, walk in pantry and top-of-the-line appliances—including an LG refrigerator, Whirlpool microwave, dishwasher, and range—await your culinary creations. Stay refreshed with the convenience of an Ultra G reverse osmosis water filter under the sink, complemented by a water filtration system that filters water for the entire house. Escape to the screened lanai and expansive yard where your private backyard oasis awaits. Whether you're hosting gatherings with friends and family or unwinding after a long day, this outdoor retreat is sure to become your favorite spot to relax and recharge. New pavers and a white vinyl privacy fence encloses your sanctuary, so you can enjoy the peace and tranquility of your own little piece of paradise.  Retreat to the primary suite, boasting a recessed ceiling, his and hers walk-in closets, and crown moldings. Pamper yourself in the spa-like bathroom, featuring a double vanity and a luxurious walk-in shower.  Elevating your lifestyle to the next level, this home is equipped with a comprehensive solar system, boasting 27 solar panels to bid farewell to power bills. Smart features abound, from keyless entry to a smart thermostat, Ring security camera system, and home surge protector, ensuring effortless living and peace of mind.    Situated in the desirable Rock Springs Farms community, just minutes from downtown St Augustine and Crescent Beach, enjoy resort-style amenities including a community pool, playground, and a scenic walking path. With no CDD fees and no flood insurance required, seize the opportunity to make this coveted Dalton model by DR Horton your own. Schedule your showing today and experience the epitome of modern living firsthand!
